# NOAA CUDEM 1/9 arc-sec, all US coastal regions. Run from pipelines/:  just ../sources/cudem/
# Streaming model: register every tile in NOAA's urllist as a /vsis3/ reference
# (reads headers only — no 188 GB download). Aggregation range-reads the COGs from
# S3. Tiles are already COGs (NAVD88 / NAD83), so no normalize/datum/tarball.
[no-cd]
default:
    uv run python source_register_remote_urllist.py cudem
